import {
  GridItem,
  Heading,
  Text,
  Box,
  SimpleGrid,
  Center,
  Stack,
} from '@chakra-ui/layout'
import React from 'react'

import AspectCard from './AspectCard'
import AspectCardJalaine from './AspectCardJalaine'
import AspectCardMariela from './AspectCardMariela'
import AspectCardBruce from './AspectCardBruce'

function Homepage() {
  return (
    <>
      <GridItem colStart={1} colSpan={4}>
        <Center>
          <Box maxW='36rem'>
            <Heading fontWeight={'light'}>The Classical Period Maya </Heading>
            <Stack direction={'row-reverse'}>
              <Text
                textAlign='right'
                fontWeight={'semibold'}
                fontStyle={'oblique'}
              >
                250 - 900 C.E.
              </Text>
              <Text></Text>
            </Stack>
          </Box>
        </Center>
        <SimpleGrid columns={{ xl: 1, lg: 2, sm: 1 }}>
          <AspectCard />
          <AspectCardJalaine />
          <AspectCardMariela />
          <AspectCardBruce />
        </SimpleGrid>
      </GridItem>
    </>
  )
}

export default Homepage
